title: Chrisette Michele Interview and More

description:
Wednesday 11/2 - Today on the show we had Chrisette Michele come by to address the miscarriage rumors, depression and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Papa Johns for blaming NFL protest for poor pizza sales and Angela helps some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
